dct_title_s: The central and western provinces of Colombia with corrections from the surveys of Mr. R. Blake White, C.E., to illustrate Mr. White's paper in the Proceedings, R.G.S. May 1883
dct_description_sm: Province and international boundaries are shown. Eastern Panama [part of Colombia] is shown. Relief shown by hachures. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 5 (1885), no. 5, pp. 249-67; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
